{"tid":790552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"太帥所以沒拒絕！ 熟女看屋跟房仲嘿咻反悔告性侵","createTime":"2018-08-23T06:05:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-23T06:22:15.000Z","uid":75969,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d00ba2f74b3a9e45905306138a81bfd7256ffa23","tid":790552,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T06:05:17.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕台北一名熟女去年找房仲帶她看屋，兩人卻屋內發生性關係，事後熟女提告性侵，但又說「因為看到對方長得不差，就不知為何沒有拒絕」，台北地檢署昨日將林男不起訴。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果日報》報導，這起案件發生在去年11月，這名熟女當時心情不好，找了林姓房仲帶她去看屋，林男除了看屋，還自詡心靈導師安慰熟女，兩人在主臥房發生關係。事後熟女突然提告林男性侵。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，熟女坦言因為對方長得帥「就不知為何沒有拒絕」，並說自己前往中國又被男人佔便宜，認為男人都是壞蛋，越想越不對勁決定提告。<br />\n<br />\n報導表示，林男無奈地說自己並無暴力脅迫，兩人在20天內又發生3次性關係。台北地檢署昨將林男不起訴。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/society/breakingnews/2528113\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fbreakingnews%2F2528113&d=WAyJM2esBSIt0x96w2cgdzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=ed01f210\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fbreakingnews%2F2528113&h=192c79e5\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/society/breakingnews/2528113</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實咁多台妹亂告人性侵洗唔洗付出代價？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04f3cb90946859b0cd9366fe573155042ba18c00","tid":790552,"uid":125720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T06:08:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">或</span></span>"},{"pid":"474fbba1effdba454b03f7f3e92536adabd53cd5","tid":790552,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T06:08:49.000Z","msg":"事後侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7745fe6076451d9409548b3f26c28e3bce35671d","tid":790552,"uid":78347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T06:10:36.000Z","msg":"熟女相?"},{"pid":"ba7971c0fd4f5adff1e48174a7626762f75af72a","tid":